<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM4.10">
<l>paḻaku nāṉmaṟai yiṉporu ḷāymata</l>
<l>moḻuku vāraṇa muyya vaḷittavem</l>
<l>aḻaka ṉāraṇi yāycciyar cintaiyuḷ</l>
<l>kuḻaka ṉārvaril kūṭiṭu kūṭalē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O circle! [You] be joined if</l>
<l rend="indent">our Handsome [Lord] who protected the elephant dripping with musth</l>
<l rend="indent">so that [it] was saved,</l>
<l rend="indent">being the Meaning of the four ancient Vedas that [everyone] practises.</l>
<l rend="indent">the youthful Man [who lives] in the thoughts of the beautiful cowherdesses,</l>
<l>will come.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
